300
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,000
I didn't.

301
00:16:37,510 --> 00:16:38,270
You didn't?

302
00:16:38,680 --> 00:16:39,800
Then what's going on here?

303
00:16:40,800 --> 00:16:41,590
He Jiashu.

304
00:16:42,310 --> 00:16:44,400
Do you still want to go to North China University?

305
00:16:44,870 --> 00:16:46,230
I've never thought about North China University.

306
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:47,680
That's all in your head.

307
00:16:49,510 --> 00:16:50,000
Okay.

308
00:16:51,270 --> 00:16:52,270
I'm afraid I can't sign

309
00:16:52,630 --> 00:16:53,190
for you

310
00:16:53,800 --> 00:16:54,480
if you have that attitude.

311
00:16:55,040 --> 00:16:56,000
So what?

312
00:16:56,550 --> 00:16:57,590
Anyway, you're not my dad.

313
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:58,510
You're in no position to control me.

314
00:16:59,550 --> 00:17:00,230
Stop right there.

315
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:02,950
Where are you going?

316
00:17:03,590 --> 00:17:04,440
Kneeling in the ancestral hall.

317
00:17:04,870 --> 00:17:05,870
You'll only give me this punishment, won't you?

318
00:17:06,800 --> 00:17:07,590
You don't need to say that.

319
00:17:08,190 --> 00:17:09,000
I'll go alone.

320
00:17:09,550 --> 00:17:10,000
Come back.

321
00:17:12,590 --> 00:17:13,830
Come back.

322
00:17:27,140 --> 00:17:30,020
[Final paper. He Hongguang]

323
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,120
I don't know

324
00:17:43,800 --> 00:17:45,680
why you're always so reluctant to compromise.

325
00:17:47,310 --> 00:17:48,630
You'd save yourself a lot of trouble

326
00:17:48,630 --> 00:17:49,950
if you'd just compromise,

327
00:17:50,510 --> 00:17:51,310
you know?

328
00:17:52,080 --> 00:17:52,590
Got it.

329
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:54,870
Thanks for signing for me.

330
00:17:57,190 --> 00:17:58,440
You're just

331
00:17:58,590 --> 00:18:00,040
too stubborn.

332
00:18:01,080 --> 00:18:03,040
I always thought you were like someone.

333
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:03,800
Who could I be like?

334
00:18:04,080 --> 00:18:04,760
It's got to be you.

335
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:05,550
You...

336
00:18:06,040 --> 00:18:06,510
What did you say?

337
00:18:06,510 --> 00:18:06,910
Uncle.

338
00:18:07,080 --> 00:18:07,950
I'm going back to study.

339
00:18:07,950 --> 00:18:09,080
I'm going to join him.

340
00:18:16,550 --> 00:18:17,190
Like me?

341
00:18:17,360 --> 00:18:17,870
Uncle.

342
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:19,950
To be honest,

343
00:18:20,760 --> 00:18:22,230
at that time, I even secretly thought

344
00:18:22,230 --> 00:18:24,000
that it would be great if you were my father,

345
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:31,310
but I didn't realize

346
00:18:31,950 --> 00:18:32,550
that I

347
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:37,510
couldn't even be the son of the He family.

348
00:18:41,510 --> 00:18:42,190
Uncle.

349
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:46,040
I know you hate me,

350
00:18:48,080 --> 00:18:49,160
but I have no reason to hate you.

351
00:18:54,630 --> 00:18:56,040
Why did you

352
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:57,950
come back this time?

353
00:19:01,630 --> 00:19:02,440
My mom died,

354
00:19:02,830 --> 00:19:03,550
so I have to cancel her account.

355
00:19:09,800 --> 00:19:10,480
Apart from that,

356
00:19:11,760 --> 00:19:12,550
there's another reason.

357
00:19:13,230 --> 00:19:13,950
It has to do with Jiahao.

358
00:19:13,950 --> 00:19:15,720
Jiahao has nothing to do with you,

359
00:19:17,550 --> 00:19:19,400
and neither does the He family.

360
00:19:23,270 --> 00:19:23,870
I know,

361
00:19:26,230 --> 00:19:28,000
but Jiahao is related to you,

362
00:19:28,830 --> 00:19:30,720
so I need to tell you.

363
00:19:33,230 --> 00:19:34,040
Jiahao

364
00:19:35,870 --> 00:19:37,550
has persistent symptoms of depression,

365
00:19:39,870 --> 00:19:41,550
and the doctor has prescribed medication for him.

366
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:43,310
These days,

367
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:44,550
I took him to do some exercise

368
00:19:44,800 --> 00:19:45,480
and training

369
00:19:46,120 --> 00:19:47,870
to help him recover and heal,

370
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:50,080
but that alone was not enough.

371
00:19:50,680 --> 00:19:51,720
What Hao needs

372
00:19:51,910 --> 00:19:53,680
is the support and understanding of his family.

373
00:19:55,310 --> 00:19:55,950
Uncle.

374
00:19:58,310 --> 00:20:00,720
Too many people in this family are already unhappy,

375
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,590
so I don't want Hao to be either.

376
00:20:13,040 --> 00:20:14,160
You said I hated you,

377
00:20:16,720 --> 00:20:17,400
but you were wrong.

378
00:20:19,720 --> 00:20:20,400
I don't hate you

379
00:20:23,630 --> 00:20:24,870
because, to me,

380
00:20:26,190 --> 00:20:27,590
you're just a stranger.

381
00:20:30,400 --> 00:20:32,360
I don't want a stranger

382
00:20:32,360 --> 00:20:34,000
to interfere with my son's life.

383
00:20:36,830 --> 00:20:38,120
I know

384
00:20:38,630 --> 00:20:39,190
Hao is depressed,

385
00:20:40,190 --> 00:20:41,630
but he's the way he is

386
00:20:41,630 --> 00:20:42,830
because of you.

387
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:47,000
He feels sorry for you,

388
00:20:49,190 --> 00:20:50,870
so he's been feeling guilty until now.

389
00:20:54,950 --> 00:20:56,230
Only if you leave

390
00:20:57,870 --> 00:20:59,270
can this be over

391
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:01,440
and Hao get better.

392
00:21:02,630 --> 00:21:04,040
As his father,

393
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:05,680
I'm grateful to you

394
00:21:06,510 --> 00:21:07,360
for being there for him these days,

395
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:09,680
but this has to end here.

396
00:21:10,830 --> 00:21:12,270
Hao doesn't need you

397
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:14,360
in his future life.

398
00:21:16,910 --> 00:21:18,080
You also said

399
00:21:19,160 --> 00:21:20,510
you are not the son of the He family,

400
00:21:21,800 --> 00:21:22,440
so we

401
00:21:25,440 --> 00:21:26,510
are not a family.

402
00:21:44,080 --> 00:21:44,950
I have some money.

403
00:21:45,480 --> 00:21:46,040
Take it.

404
00:21:47,230 --> 00:21:49,510
Please leave Xiqiao

405
00:21:49,950 --> 00:21:51,480
and Hao

406
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:54,720
with your real father forever.

407
00:22:08,800 --> 00:22:09,440
Shu.

408
00:22:12,550 --> 00:22:13,680
I beg you.

409
00:23:11,120 --> 00:23:11,550
Uncle.

410
00:23:15,440 --> 00:23:15,870
Uncle.

411
00:23:16,680 --> 00:23:17,680
Why aren't you in bed?

412
00:23:19,080 --> 00:23:19,870
Your aunt doesn't allow me

413
00:23:20,120 --> 00:23:21,480
to smoke in the room.

414
00:23:23,360 --> 00:23:24,310
Why are you awake?

415
00:23:24,310 --> 00:23:26,120
Did Hao keep you from sleeping?

416
00:23:26,120 --> 00:23:26,870
He didn't.

417
00:23:26,870 --> 00:23:28,000
I just came out to drink some water.

418
00:23:29,230 --> 00:23:30,160
Thanks for taking care

419
00:23:30,480 --> 00:23:31,720
of Hao these days.

420
00:23:32,080 --> 00:23:33,120
Hao is my cousin,

421
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:34,590
so I should take care of him.

422
00:23:46,590 --> 00:23:47,040
Uncle.

423
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:49,550
Thank you for taking me in.

424
00:23:51,870 --> 00:23:53,120
Don't thank me.

425
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:55,270
We're family,

426
00:23:55,830 --> 00:23:56,870
so this is your home.

427
00:23:57,550 --> 00:23:58,630
It's not like taking you in.

428
00:24:01,190 --> 00:24:02,310
I don't usually

429
00:24:02,310 --> 00:24:03,830
have a good temper,

430
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:06,190
so if I've done something wrong,

431
00:24:07,630 --> 00:24:08,680
just bear with me.

432
00:24:13,760 --> 00:24:14,440
Uncle.

433
00:24:17,980 --> 00:24:18,500
Thank you.

434
00:24:27,700 --> 00:24:29,780
[Agricultural Bank of China]

