438
00:24:44,310 --> 00:24:46,480
"I am He Jiashu's real father."

439
00:24:48,830 --> 00:24:49,950
Hearing this,

440
00:24:50,080 --> 00:24:51,630
He Jiashu knew that this would prove that he was born

441
00:24:51,630 --> 00:24:53,510
