443
00:24:56,510 --> 00:24:57,830
He was really cruel.

444
00:24:57,910 --> 00:24:59,120
That was his real dad,

445
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:00,870
but He Jiashu

446
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:02,630
showed no mercy.

447
00:25:03,120 --> 00:25:04,040
And he

448
00:25:04,510 --> 00:25:05,830
