00:28:24,630 --> 00:28:25,400
Or you can

514
00:28:25,720 --> 00:28:26,440
take a nap

515
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:27,120
or rest for a while.

516
00:28:29,120 --> 00:28:30,040
Don't play with your cell phone.

