541
00:29:56,160 --> 00:29:57,040
and beat you up.

542
00:30:16,950 --> 00:30:17,360
Junli.

543
00:30:17,360 --> 00:30:17,800
Do you want it?

544
00:30:18,510 --> 00:30:19,000
No.

545
00:30:21,510 --> 00:30:22,480
Have you seen him

546
00:30:22,910 --> 00:30:23,760
