563
00:30:54,760 --> 00:30:55,760
He does nothing but study

564
00:30:55,760 --> 00:30:57,040
at home every day.

565
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:58,950
He must be going crazy,

566
00:30:59,400 --> 00:30:59,870
right?

567
00:31:02,830 --> 00:31:03,160
You don't want it?

